data.description: ATTENTION BUYERS!  This spacious .47-acre lot offers plenty of space for multiple opportunities. The City has suggested there is a potential of adding an ADU (buyers do due diligence). Located near North Medford High School, this 1443 sq/ft home has 3 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. Step inside to the inviting living room and dining room which features 3/4'' hardwood flooring. Newly installed French doors that create a seamless transition between the primary bedroom and the backyard. Another bedroom also features its own French doors leading to the backyard. All bedrooms are good size & one bedroom (and hallway) has new carpet. The yard offers a sense of privacy, a newer shed & ample space for RV parking. Seller will contribute up to $2,500 towards closing costs, pre-paids and rate buy down.
